              </li>
              <li>
                  <a href="http://rubyonrails.org/" target="_blank">Ruby on Rails</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                  <a href="https://github.com/hatem/" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                  <a target="_blank" href="http://www.espace.com.eg/">eSpace</a>
